bellsouthpwp/Groups/15/15568/pages/34736/Kimaya-60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Regaurding wizard council</span><hr size=1> I've actually been kicking around the idea for a guild for pure casters for a while now.  However, I decided that with the small population, I'd rather form a guild that's more inclusive to expand the resources for all concerned.  Maybe that's because I'm a druid.  *grin*<br><br>So now I'm working on a guild idea called Twilight Bastion.  The intent is to have a neutral &quot;safe haven&quot; for everyone to pursue their studies in peace and/or fight against the Light/Dark wars that threaten that peace.  It's all about banding together as individuals so we can all accomplish our goals without demanding others share them.<br><br>Anyway, my hope is to have a Wizards Council, a Magicians Circle, an Enchanters Enclave and a Necromancers Coterie within this guild, as well as warrior, druid, cleric, etc. backup to help garner resources for research, etc.  (Yes, I did say I'm a druid, but I still love research. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    )<br><br>My question is: would you casters be interested?  I already have one wizard who's working with me on it, but I'll need a lot more interested casters to provide them with the kind of community I envision.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Edit:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> I decided I would actually throw in a little &quot;pleeeease consider this!&quot; begging.  What I REALLY want is for there to be enough within each casters' circle that they can have their own inner mysteries that no one else in the guild knows about -- a real community with its own subsets and secrets.  I'd even help write them!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p>---<BR>Kimaya Silverbark<BR><BR>"I bark at that!"</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukimayasilverbark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kimaya Silverbark</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.alienexplorer.com/clipart/images5/wolf.pawprint2.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/18/02 8:22:29 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udeneteth1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deneteth1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 88<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/18/02 10:07:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Regaurding wizard council</span><hr size=1> I shall never ally myself with necromancers. Evil should be destroyed at all costs you fools.<br><br>/ooc Artillis already started this discussion about a wizard only guild ages ago as I recall but too few of us answered the call at the time.<br>A caster guild would be nice but from an RP point of view I cannot enter an organization that would accept dark casters in its ranks, sorry.<br><br>Deneteth Wintermist<br>31th wizard, follower of Mithaniel Marr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udunnar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dunnar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/18/02 11:04:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Regaurding wizard council</span><hr size=1> As a good and upstanding Wizard I 2nd that.<br><br>I would be happy to be a part of a enchanter, wizard and Mage circle. <p>Zapoo the Wise<BR>Wizard of Tinker's Pride<BR>zapoo@tinkerspride.com<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukimayasilverbark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kimaya Silverbark</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.alienexplorer.com/clipart/images5/wolf.pawprint2.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 78<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/18/02 11:38:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.bellsouth.net/coDataImages/bellsouthpwp/Groups/15/15568/pages/34736/Kimaya-60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Regaurding wizard council</span><hr size=1> ...and I suppose that's why I'm having to make my own neutral guild!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Edit:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Okay, that may have sounded snotty, which wasn't my intent.  But when I get the charter posted, please read it anyway to see if it changes any in-character minds about what is more important ~ destruction waged over conflicts between the factions of good and evil, or the freedom to research and share knowledge for the benefit of all.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p>---<BR>Kimaya Silverbark<BR><BR>"I bark at that!"</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukimayasilverbark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kimaya Silverbark</A>