e and i'm still kicking it aroud but I don't know how many of you would be interested in that becase.....<br><br>1. Only wizards (adds to roleplay of it, ya caster specific is ok but i'm too partial to wizards, sorry mages and enchanters <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   ).<br><br>2. I't would be a 50+ guild with possibilties of apprentices (lower level wizards) to wizards.<br><br>3. Yes it would all be roleplayed, Already have thought of guild structure, rules, meetings, roleplaying meetings, innitiations, and more.<br><br>4. Becase it would be an all wizard guild and high end it would operate in a fashion similar to a mercenary guild were it would alow all wizards of any race and would assist other guilds in raids.  It would be a guild formed for the unity of wizardry thus petty disagrements or racial differances would be set aside &quot;within&quot; the guild for the betterment of wizardry as a whole.  however fights between dark elf wizard and a high elf wizard would be tollerated, just not at mettings.  It would not govern racial differances or arguments, just that they would be put on hold when needed for sake of knowledge and enlightenment.<br><br>5. Popultaion of it would be low, becase heck, how many 50+ wizards do you even see out there. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    More importantly, how many 50+ wizards do you see NOT in a guild already, and willing to leave it to pull something like this off?<br><br>6. Many are afraid a all wizard group or raid wouldn't work and that you have to have clerics, enchanters and meat sheilds to do anything <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   .  Standard holy trinity group.  But then on the flip side 18 (3 groups of 6) wizards all 55+ going up against any ubber mob would equal one dead mob.  So what if one wizard gets beat on for 5 seconds as his eppic skin or manaskin gets eaten away while the other 17 wizards all nuke at once for 600+ each.  Becase the 51+ draught line has such a very short cast time as long as all the wizards worked together they could keep from having many deaths, heck can always hire a cleric to tag along and tell them any thing that drops that is not wizard usable is yours.<br><br>Some may ask why high end?  Well wizards start to realy gain power and come into their own in the high end game.  I've heard it said many times, wizards are great at soloing and raiding and not so great for exp grinds.  Wizards have power but once they hit 51 and up, they shine.<br><br>So basicaly becase of all those listed things the whole idea went on hold, if you look down the forum here you'll probably see a post i made a while back about wanting to start this.<br><br>Anyway back to the topic at hand will have to set up anouther time to have a wizard meeting.  I still think sometime on a sunday would be best.  Don't care what time just as long as we get people there. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uartillis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Artillis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0> at: 1/18/02 2:22:07 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udeneteth1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deneteth1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 89<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/18/02 7:37:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Regaurding wizard council</span><hr size=1> /oo